    <item>
      <title>KKR 220 亿欧元收购意大利电信交易获欧盟批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/kkr-s-22-billion-telecom-italia-deal-wins-unconditional-eu-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR &amp; Co. 以 220 亿欧元（238 亿美元）收购意大利电信 (Telecom Italia SpA) 固定电话网络的提议已获得欧盟早期批准，为这家前电话垄断企业放弃其最有价值资产的控制权铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/kkr-s-22-billion-telecom-italia-deal-wins-unconditional-eu-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大皇家银行资本市场部门利润创历史新高，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rbc-tops-estimates-as-profit-surges-in-capital-markets-division</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行在完成了对汇丰控股有限公司加拿大业务的里程碑式交易后，凭借公司资本市场业务的强劲表现和低于预期的潜在贷款损失准备金，其业绩超出了分析师的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rbc-tops-estimates-as-profit-surges-in-capital-markets-division</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 10:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标普 500 指数定价在 GDP 日出现故障后恢复：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经济数据显示经济增长势头放缓之后，全球最大的股市遭遇定价故障，导致股市下跌、债市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 22:23:24 GMT</pubDate>
